Package oogasalad.engine.controller

Class DefaultGameController

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.engine.controller.DefaultGameController
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameControllerAPI, GameExecutor, GameObjectProvider
public class DefaultGameController extends Object implements GameControllerAPI, GameObjectProvider, GameExecutor
Default implementation of the GameControllerAPI.

This class is responsible for managing game objects, loading level data, and updating the game state based on the loaded data. It delegates file handling to an EngineFileConverterAPI and stores a local list of GameObjects that represent the current game state.

Author:
Alana Zinkin
